{"tid":331937,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【乃木坂46】 十八單＜逃げ水＞MV 讀後感","createTime":"2017-07-22T14:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T07:14:20.000Z","uid":1098,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2837200c2402e9e99bb7cbdfe860e47939abbf4","tid":331937,"uid":1098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://aikru.com/file/parts/2822/ddbd9f204a26514b298bd616c1ba9e58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Faikru.com%2Ffile%2Fparts%2F2822%2Fddbd9f204a26514b298bd616c1ba9e58.jpg&h=8f25635d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當我睇完&lt;逃げ水&gt;個mv，腦海立即彈出幾個字：「一念無明、The Mad World」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係講笑。我諗大家睇個MV都會有哩種感覺：啲人係咪痴線㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFOtiQoVwAAR0qt.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFOtiQoVwAAR0qt.jpg%3Alarge&h=e814d5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMV入面伊丹家啲人個個都做埋曬啲好奇怪嘅行為。<br />\n<br />\n有人會為早餐食乜而鬥爭（蝸角之爭）、有人會明眀係日本人又強行扮中國人（身份認同）、有人執着禮節，要房間永遠保持乾淨（強逼症、道德撚）、有人做OL做到返屋企都繼續做，搞到變成鬼魂（工作壓力、過勞死）、有人將自己困喺間房，覺得冇人明白自己（宅男現象）、亦有人打扮另類，用電動車代步（反叛、潮童）.........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/matome1206-nogizaka46matomenoma/imgs/8/2/822d769a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fmatome1206-nogizaka46matomenoma%2Fimgs%2F8%2F2%2F822d769a.jpg&h=21526c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>每個人都有一種病，每個人都受角色定型影響住。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFVfnHnUMAAxWrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFVfnHnUMAAxWrz.jpg&h=d37bc444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事入面最想脫離角色嘅係<ins>飛鳥</ins>，但係佢亦無辦法真正解放，睇清自己真實嘅一面，只能扮受傷去逃避社會畀佢嘅角色。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而種種嘅嘢都呼應住首歌：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">海市蜃樓</span></strong><br />\n所有人都只睇到社會規範，但哩啲只係幻象，冇人睇得清每個人、每樣事物嘅實相。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFOld8AVYAAvZYk.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFOld8AVYAAvZYk.jpg%3Alarge&h=9dd9b79a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而去到音樂嘅最後，舞蹈嘅動作係<em>跪低、掩眼、雙手合十</em>，似乎就係反映住要用清淨嘅心先能夠睇到實相。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但隨住舞蹈結束，就出現一個耐人尋味嘅twist：<strong>兩個婢女瞓緊教</strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFOld7-VoAIAz48.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFOld7-VoAIAz48.jpg%3Alarge&h=cea7d5f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇交代佢地係幾時瞓着，不過可以見到佢地隔離有塊布，瞓喺走廊度，似乎就係故事開始冇幾耐（食早餐之後），佢地抹地嗰陣瞓着咗。<br />\n<br />\n咁會唔會表示，其實佢地抹地個scene 之後嘅嘢都係夢境嚟㗎呢？如果係，咁就即係成個故事都只係幻象嚟，連觀眾都呃埋。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係夢，或者亦可以理解為佢地對社會上嘅「瘋子」感到好厭倦，寧願去瞓教。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總而言之，成個mv就係講緊幻象同實相，人要用心去睇清事物。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申：睇完第一次之後彈咗好多諗法出嚟，之後再睇咗幾次，然後見到個人物設定之後感受更深</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n小小愚見，歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93418a7afc28e60b212895eccd1cb54d971154d","tid":331937,"uid":20114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:47:56.000Z","msg":"支持飛青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁到癲"},{"pid":"dced6c726b0ea6677dd4e7d1c9b065a3b975d121","tid":331937,"uid":25375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:49:20.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6683cf5bf4b23d00c720217bf3f6acadbc6e9f1","tid":331937,"uid":3769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"唔洗深究肥秋團嘅MV故事是常識吧"},{"pid":"1a8c8d3dc88f297c11515a0c7666f5f65c0d02f4","tid":331937,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:25:06.000Z","msg":"界爛條裙屌打呢個"},{"pid":"085210c90b2c6e095bf0f4b386702cc6a80b52e1","tid":331937,"uid":2040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:27:26.000Z","msg":"ching ho ball‼️<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ea24440a0c2b66b8df874a4d6262d22c95c8b8","tid":331937,"uid":1098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>界爛條裙屌打呢個</blockquote><br />\n欅本身已經set咗成個世界觀，無得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362d0c5e43037d1ffb14276169bea55aa9413417","tid":331937,"uid":1098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗深究肥秋團嘅MV故事是常識吧</blockquote><br />\n我都知，不過今次呢個特別有感受就講下，當係吹下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eca9f998f059825b4cac9839459b25369e4acc2","tid":331937,"uid":20114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:39:29.000Z","msg":"高質幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557c86c50b63c2856deede234186baddf3e75bdd","tid":331937,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"可能我低質 但覺得呢個mv麻麻<br />\n由其是推新人 整到咁魔幻好咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cee66f78071353ab2958a0ade965374f8fc9d5","tid":331937,"uid":1098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能我低質 但覺得呢個mv麻麻<br />\n由其是推新人 整到咁魔幻好咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個人覺得呢個MV冇當兩個center係主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}